<text><body>
<lb n="0411a11"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0411a12"/>
<lb n="0411a13"/><head type="no">No. 981</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0411a14"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0411001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】保安四年寫仁和寺藏本，【乙】高山寺藏古寫本</note>大毘盧遮那佛眼修行儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0411a15"/>
<lb n="0411a16"/><byline type="Author">沙門一行述記</byline>
<lb n="0411a17"/><p>爾時不動明王。執持慧刀威猛奮怒。相其所
<lb n="0411a18"/>赴方面畫作雲龍。以大慧刀印而斷壞之。彼
<lb n="0411a19"/>障即時消散。所以然者。世人於空露地畫作
<lb n="0411a20"/>漫荼羅時。若遇惡龍降雨即便毀壞。行者於
<lb n="0411a21"/>心地中畫作大悲漫荼羅。亦復如是。若為三
<lb n="0411a22"/>毒惡龍降暴雨流駛水。令不思議染色湮滅
<lb n="0411a23"/>湮淪故。用無垢智身作不動明王。威猛大勢
<lb n="0411a24"/>以慧刀印斷壞陰雲。則隨所向之方無不清
<lb n="0411a25"/>廓也。招<note place="inline">引</note>羅<note n="0411002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">劍＝&CB00669;【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411002"><lem>劍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00669;</rdg></app>是金剛橛。首如一股金剛。而
<lb n="0411a26"/>下體銛銳。猶如橛形。若更細小者名金剛針。
<lb n="0411a27"/>其相各異。阿闍梨建立漫荼羅。時或勇建菩
<lb n="0411a28"/>提心。依金剛橛方便以息風雨。當用佉陀羅
<lb n="0411a29"/>木。若無者當用苦<note n="0411003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">楝＝練【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411003"><lem>楝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">練</rdg></app>木乃至<note n="0411004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鑌＝賓【乙】</note><app n="0411004"><lem>鑌</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">賓</rdg></app>鐵為之。用
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0411b" n="0411b"/>
<lb n="0411b01"/>成<app><lem>辦</lem><rdg wit="【大】">辨</rdg></app>諸事金剛薩埵加持。觀自身即同一切
<lb n="0411b02"/>金剛。以<note n="0411005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">釘＝針【乙】</note><app n="0411005"><lem>釘</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">針</rdg></app>障起方面。則令道場地分一切
<lb n="0411b03"/>皆同金剛。是故諸障無能嬈害。即結契定慧
<lb n="0411b04"/>金剛合掌。屈二頭指。以指頭向下。<note n="0411006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋二【乙】</note><app n="0411006"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">以二</rdg></app>大指
<lb n="0411b05"/>各捻頭<note n="0411007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">指＋（之）【乙】</note><app n="0411007"><lem>指</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">指之</rdg></app>傍。以印置心誦真言三遍。頂散
<lb n="0411b06"/>之。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0411b07"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三曼多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0411008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃＝南【甲】</note><app n="0411008"><lem>喃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">南</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0411002"><lem>劍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&CB00669;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0411b08"/><p>次當觀威猛大勢不動明王住本曼荼羅位
<lb n="0411b09"/>中。即是三角<note n="0411009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漫＝曼【乙】</note><app n="0411009"><lem>漫</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">曼</rdg></app>荼羅周匝熾焰。其中微黑是
<lb n="0411b10"/>也。此有二種。或觀聖不動尊住本位中。以三
<lb n="0411b11"/>昧足蹈彼頂上。或觀自身即是不動尊。<note n="0411010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋住【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411010"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">亦住</rdg></app>本
<lb n="0411b12"/>位之中。以三昧足加彼頂上。臨以忿怒之威。
<lb n="0411b13"/>隨彼諸為障者即當退散。若固爾不從教命
<lb n="0411b14"/>不速去者。必當自絕其命。是持真言者。當生
<lb n="0411b15"/>慈心勿令彼命根斷絕也。所以然者。如是淨
<lb n="0411b16"/>菩提心不動明王。殺害諸眾生業煩惱壽命
<lb n="0411b17"/>時。即須生彼法性真常之命故。若諸佛令修
<lb n="0411b18"/>行者。必定墮於灰斷涅槃者。便有殺眾生罪
<lb n="0411b19"/>故。不應如文堅<note n="0411011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">執＝住【乙】</note><app n="0411011"><lem>執</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>。而失如來密意也。</p>
<lb n="0411b20"/><p>次行者應入威怒降三世明王觀。淨除<note n="0411012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自我＝內外【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411012"><lem>自我</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">內外</rdg></app>
<lb n="0411b21"/>所生障。二羽交臂金剛拳。檀慧相<note n="0411013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鉤＝句【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411013"><lem>鉤</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">句</rdg></app>。&CB00594;進
<lb n="0411b22"/>力。是其契法。行者即想身發威焰。八臂四面
<lb n="0411b23"/>&CB00594;利牙。虎吼吽字如雷音。頂上右旋成結界。
<lb n="0411b24"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0411b25"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0411014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（一）夾註【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411014"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>遜<note place="inline">蘇<note n="0411015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＝甚【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411015"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">甚</rdg></app>反下同</note>婆&CB00135;遜婆吽<note place="inline"><note n="0411016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝二【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411016"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note><note n="0411017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吃＝紇【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411017"><lem>吃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">紇</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合下同</note>&CB00617;拏
<lb n="0411b26"/><app type="＊" source="0411017"><lem>吃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">紇</rdg></app>哩&CB00617;拏吽<note place="inline"><note n="0411018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝三【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411018"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app></note><app type="＊" source="0411017"><lem>吃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">紇</rdg></app><note n="0411019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哩＋（二合）夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411019"><lem>哩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">哩<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>&CB00617;拏<note n="0411020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411020"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>播耶吽<note place="inline">四</note>阿
<lb n="0411b27"/>難耶斛<note place="inline">五</note>薄伽梵&CB00085;日羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0411021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吽＋（引）夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411021"><lem>吽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吽<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>發<note n="0411022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒＋（六）夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411022"><lem>吒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吒<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0411b28"/><p>即入金剛忿怒威光熾盛三世<note n="0411023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（無）＋勝【乙】</note><app n="0411023"><lem>勝</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">無勝</rdg></app>三摩地。菩
<lb n="0411b29"/>薩有四面皆忿怒。八臂各執器杖。左足蹈<note n="0411024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【乙】</note><app n="0411024"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0411c" n="0411c"/>
<lb n="0411c01"/>自在天。右足蹈烏摩<note n="0411025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔妃〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411025"><lem>妃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。如丁字勢立。遍身
<lb n="0411c02"/>火焰洞燃如劫災火。此即三世勝聖者三摩
<lb n="0411c03"/>地觀也。修行者應住發菩提心深起悲愍<note n="0411026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【乙】</note><app n="0411026"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0411c04"/>滅除內外人天等障。即以印左轉三匝辟除
<lb n="0411c05"/>障者。便右轉三匝。隨意大小結為方隅界。即
<lb n="0411c06"/>印心額喉頂每處誦一遍。頂上散印。由結此
<lb n="0411c07"/>印<note n="0411027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔及〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411027"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦真言。住此忿怒三摩地。身心所有煩
<lb n="0411c08"/>惱等業障。以金剛猛利慧火梵燒悉盡。</p>
<lb n="0411c09"/><p>次結軍荼利明王護身契。二羽相叉小指於
<lb n="0411c10"/>掌中。以二無名指雙屈入掌中。捻於二小指
<lb n="0411c11"/>叉上。合腕&CB00594;<note n="0411028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（二）＋中【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411028"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">二中</rdg></app>指頭相<note n="0411029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411029"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app>。兩頭指小屈曲。
<lb n="0411c12"/>當中指背上節後勿著之。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0411c13"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>戶嚕戶嚕<note place="inline">二</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合三</note>盤<note n="0411030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陀＋（四）夾註【乙】</note><app n="0411030"><lem>陀</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">陀<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0411c14"/>盤陀<note n="0411031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【乙】</note><app n="0411031"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>訶<note place="inline">去引</note>那訶<note place="inline">去<note n="0411032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411032"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>那<note place="inline">五</note><note n="0411033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿＝訶【甲】</note><app n="0411033"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app><note place="inline">上</note>蜜哩<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0411c15"/>帝<note place="inline">六</note>吽<note place="inline">七</note>發<note n="0411034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【甲】</note><app n="0411034"><lem><note place="inline">八</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0411c16"/><p>誦真言七遍已。若有人常欲受持金剛法者。
<lb n="0411c17"/>每日平旦洗手澡面已。即以右手掬於淨水
<lb n="0411c18"/>&CB00057;七遍已。向東方散三遍。後即入房內作護
<lb n="0411c19"/>身。其護身法者。結印不解口誦真言。印頂。次
<lb n="0411c20"/>印<note n="0411035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411035"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>肩。次印<note n="0411036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">左＝右【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411036"><lem>左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">右</rdg></app>肩。次印心前。次印頸下。次
<lb n="0411c21"/>印眉間。次印髮際。次印頂上印頂後已。是其
<lb n="0411c22"/>契法也。</p>
<lb n="0411c23"/><p>次六足尊明王印。二羽金剛內縛。二中指
<lb n="0411c24"/>直&CB00594;頭相合。舒二頭指。小曲初分如三股。加
<lb n="0411c25"/>持五處。是其印相也。謂五處者。額兩肩心喉
<lb n="0411c26"/>是。其<note n="0411037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二大＝大小二【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411037"><lem>二大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">大小二</rdg></app>指。各以右押左。叉入月中。真言
<lb n="0411c27"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0411c28"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0411014"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>枳哩<note place="inline">入二合</note>瑟怛哩<note n="0411038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入三合二＝二合【甲】，入二合【乙】</note><note n="0411038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入三合二＝二合【甲】，＝入二合【乙】</note><app n="0411038"><lem><note place="inline">入三合二</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">二合</note></rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">入二合</note></rdg></app>毘枳哩<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note n="0411039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝娜【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411039"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">娜</rdg></app>曩
<lb n="0411c29"/><note place="inline">二</note>吽薩&CB00085;遮<note n="0411040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＝&CB00418;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0411040"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00418;</rdg></app>嚕<note place="inline">二合<note n="0411041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0411041"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>娜捨也薩<note n="0411042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曇二合＝二合曇【乙】</note><app n="0411042"><lem>曇<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">二合曇</rdg></app>婆
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0412a" n="0412a"/>
<lb n="0412a01"/><note n="0412001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＝耶【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0412001"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>薩曇<note n="0412002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0412002"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>婆<app type="＊" source="0412001"><lem>野</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">耶</rdg></app><note n="0412003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0412003"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>蘇婆<note place="inline">二合</note>吒蘇婆<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0412a02"/>吒吽發吒娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0412a03"/><p>結此印及誦真言。即是無始無明於一切生
<lb n="0412a04"/>死中而得自在。唯<note n="0412004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412004"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>菩提心明王能制伏之。
<lb n="0412a05"/>乃至殺彼無常之身。令得常命。餘以類推之
<lb n="0412a06"/>可解也。</p>
<lb n="0412a07"/><p>次結金剛藥叉明王印。定慧金剛內縛。二頭
<lb n="0412a08"/>指端相<app type="＊" source="0411029"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">跓</rdg></app>。其間如眼。以二大指。各&CB00594;二頭
<lb n="0412a09"/>指側勿相著。各曲初節似牙。二小指各舒。其
<lb n="0412a10"/>共少許曲初節。如二牙相向。誦真言加持額
<lb n="0412a11"/>兩肩心喉。又更開五眼。所謂以印拭右左眉
<lb n="0412a12"/>目眉間是也。以印頂散之。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0412a13"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>摩訶藥乞叉<note place="inline">二</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0411041"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>惹
<lb n="0412a14"/>吽<note place="inline"><note n="0412005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（四）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412005"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">引四</rdg></app></note>&CB00680;斛<note place="inline">引<note n="0412006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝五【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412006"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app></note><note n="0412007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝波&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0412007" corr="波" resp="【原】">婆</sic>羅吠者耶<note n="0412008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412008"><lem><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引六</note>發吒
<lb n="0412a15"/><note n="0412009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412009"><lem><note place="inline">七</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0412a16"/><p>結此印及誦真言。是諸毒藥當作障礙者。向
<lb n="0412a17"/>形像而用塗之。以如是治故彼六情根。猶如
<lb n="0412a18"/>火燒即時退散。</p>
<lb n="0412a19"/><p>次結馬頭明王印。二手合掌。二頭指二無名
<lb n="0412a20"/>指屈入掌。各自相背。並二大指。微屈勿著頭
<lb n="0412a21"/>指。即誦真言。左轉三匝辟除障者。右轉三匝
<lb n="0412a22"/>成為結界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0412a23"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0412010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412010"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿<note n="0412011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412011"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>哩&CB00107;納婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;吽<note place="inline">引</note>發吒娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0412a24"/><note n="0412012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二引合〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412012"><lem><note place="inline">二引合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>賀<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0412a25"/><p>結此印及誦真言。辛毒之藥。即是無常苦空
<lb n="0412a26"/>無我等。苦切對治。譬如病氣深入心<note n="0412013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瞑＝湎【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412013"><lem>瞑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">湎</rdg></app>眩。
<lb n="0412a27"/>故之乃可盡其<note n="0412014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本源＝源本【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412014"><lem>本源</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">源本</rdg></app>。乃至帝釋梵王等。自在
<lb n="0412a28"/>安樂為世界之尊。如來以此法治之。即悟心
<lb n="0412a29"/>身熾然猶如火害。厭怖生死。正順涅槃。何況
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0412b" n="0412b"/>
<lb n="0412b01"/>餘有情耶。</p>
<lb n="0412b02"/><p>次結無能<note n="0412015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔勝〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412015"><lem>勝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>明王根本祕密印。二羽虛心合
<lb n="0412b03"/>掌。十輪端相<note n="0412016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】＊，柱【乙】＊</note><note n="0412016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄＝跓【甲】＊，＝柱【乙】＊</note><app n="0412016"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">柱</rdg></app>令密合。是<note n="0412017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【甲】</note><app n="0412017"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>印相也。</p>
<lb n="0412b04"/><p>真言<note place="inline">在別由極密而暫不注之</note>。</p>
<lb n="0412b05"/><p>由結此印及誦真言<note n="0412018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412018"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。諸障盡息。令如來正
<lb n="0412b06"/>三昧耶種種教&CB00330;。一切無能隱蔽之者。</p>
<lb n="0412b07"/><p>復次以<app type="＊" source="0411036"><lem>左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">右</rdg></app>手掌。仰覆<app type="＊" source="0411035"><lem>右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">左</rdg></app>手<note n="0412019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔掌〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412019"><lem>掌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>上。以<app type="＊" source="0411035"><lem>右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">左</rdg></app>手
<lb n="0412b08"/>大指。押<app type="＊" source="0411036"><lem>左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">右</rdg></app>大指甲上。以右頭指三度彈指。
<lb n="0412b09"/>次<note n="0412020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔屈〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412020"><lem>屈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>握於左右手頭指以下四指。&CB00594;大母指。
<lb n="0412b10"/>以右<note n="0412021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔手〕－【乙】</note><app n="0412021"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>印。左旋三遍為辟除。右旋三遍為結
<lb n="0412b11"/>界。次以同印。指於四方<anchor id="fxT19p0412b05"/>四角上下二方。即
<lb n="0412b12"/>印身五處。皆誦每處吽字真言加持也。</p>
<lb n="0412b13"/><p>次結一字佛頂明王印。二羽內相叉作拳。&CB00594;
<lb n="0412b14"/>二中指。屈上節如<app type="＊" source="0411002"><lem>劍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&CB00669;</rdg></app>形。並<note n="0412022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">立＝&CB00594;【乙】</note><app n="0412022"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00594;</rdg></app>二大指。屈二
<lb n="0412b15"/>頭指。捻二<note n="0412023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝頭【甲】</note><app n="0412023"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">頭</rdg></app>指上節即是。以印加持五處。
<lb n="0412b16"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0412b17"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三漫多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>喃部嚕唵<note place="inline"><note n="0412024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【乙】</note><app n="0412024"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>合</note></p>
<lb n="0412b18"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。一切惡鬼皆不敢近
<lb n="0412b19"/>此&CB00057;<note n="0412025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔師〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412025"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。所護自身。所護他人。所呼鬼神。所
<lb n="0412b20"/>遣鬼神。所求事業。並用此&CB00057;。若持誦&CB00057;無有
<lb n="0412b21"/>神驗。為誦此&CB00057;一百八遍。即得成就所得境
<lb n="0412b22"/>界。若無&CB00283;驗其神即消滅。</p>
<lb n="0412b23"/><p>次結佛眼明<app type="＊" source="0411025"><lem>妃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。印以二手合掌。屈二頭指。
<lb n="0412b24"/>各<app type="＊" source="0412016"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>中指背。並屈二大母指入掌。以印真言
<lb n="0412b25"/>加持五處。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0412b26"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒<note n="0412026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">馱＋（引）夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412026"><lem>馱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">馱<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app><note n="0412027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃＝南【乙】＊</note><app n="0412027"><lem>喃</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">南</rdg></app>唵嚕嚕薩普<note place="inline">二合</note>嚕入
<lb n="0412b27"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>悉馱盧者寧薩&CB00085;&CB00770;他<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0412b28"/>合</note>娑達尼娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0412028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><app n="0412028"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0412b29"/><p>由結此佛眼印及誦真言故。令祕密主觸類
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0412c" n="0412c"/>
<lb n="0412c01"/>申而長之。遍於一切法中。以故名為<note n="0412029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝善&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0412029" corr="善" resp="【原】">若</sic>知
<lb n="0412c02"/>三密也。即引佛為證。何以故。世尊即一切諸
<lb n="0412c03"/>真言三<note n="0412030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昧＝摩【甲】</note><app n="0412030"><lem>昧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>耶。所謂住於自<note n="0412031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">種性＝種姓&M062485;【原】＊，性種【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0412031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>種性＝種姓&M062485;【原】＊，＝性種【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412031"><lem><sic corr="種姓" resp="【原】">種性</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">性種</rdg></app>故。譬如轉
<lb n="0412c04"/>輪聖王。若住於自種<anchor id="fxT19p0412c01"/>性中。遵修上代轉輪治
<lb n="0412c05"/>世之法無所增減。則四域之內自然恭順其
<lb n="0412c06"/>命。世尊亦爾。以常安住如來種<note n="0412032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姓＝性【乙】＊</note><app n="0412032"><lem>姓</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">性</rdg></app>之中無
<lb n="0412c07"/>所違越故。一切諸真言王。無不法而行之。以
<lb n="0412c08"/>為性平等戒。而不敢犯。復次如剎<note n="0412033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝土【乙】</note><app n="0412033"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">土</rdg></app>婆羅門
<lb n="0412c09"/>四姓。若住於自種<app type="＊" source="0412032"><lem>姓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">性</rdg></app>中奉其法。則為世人稱
<lb n="0412c10"/>舉。事有成功。今此本漫荼羅亦爾。平等無動
<lb n="0412c11"/>是金剛地。性無生性。寂靜圓滿是大悲水性
<lb n="0412c12"/>離<note n="0412034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝文【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412034"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">文</rdg></app>說性。鋒銳照明是<note n="0412035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋慧【乙】</note><app n="0412035"><lem>慧</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">大慧</rdg></app>火性離塵垢性。
<lb n="0412c13"/>卷舒成壞是自<note n="0412036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">性＝在【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412036"><lem>性</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>風性離因緣性。無相之像
<lb n="0412c14"/>是不可<note n="0412037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝得【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412037"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>空大空本性。如是本性。三世諸佛
<lb n="0412c15"/>為不能作之。何況諸為障者能蔽之。是故真
<lb n="0412c16"/>言門修菩薩行諸菩薩。亦當紹如來種性故。
<lb n="0412c17"/>效諸尊住本漫荼羅位作諸事業也。若欲作
<lb n="0412c18"/>寂災事業。即當自作本尊身而住圓漫荼羅。
<lb n="0412c19"/>若作增益事業。即住方漫荼羅。若作降伏<note n="0412038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔等〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412038"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0412c20"/>事業。即住三角漫荼羅。<note n="0412039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（若）＋欲【乙】</note><app n="0412039"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">若欲</rdg></app>作攝召事業。即
<lb n="0412c21"/>住半月漫荼羅。若欲出生種種莊嚴。即住雜
<lb n="0412c22"/>色漫荼羅。能令行者成驗即同本尊。一切為
<lb n="0412c23"/>障者無能映<note n="0412040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03033;＝奪&M062485;【原】【乙】</note><sic n="0412040" corr="奪" resp="【原】【乙】">&CB03033;</sic>也。</p>
<lb n="0412c24"/><p>次觀漫荼羅。八葉蓮華臺上。觀置種種莊嚴
<lb n="0412c25"/>漫荼羅。漫荼羅之上可觀三部海會。作是觀
<lb n="0412c26"/>已。<note n="0412041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412041"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作金剛合掌頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0412c27"/><lg><l>以我功德力</l><l>如來加持力</l>
<lb n="0412c28"/><l>及以法界力</l><l>普供養諸<note n="0412042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尊＝佛【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412042"><lem>尊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">佛</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0412c29"/><l>願生安樂<note n="0412043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">國＝剎【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0412043"><lem>國</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">剎</rdg></app></l><l>普供養而住</l></lg>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0413a" n="0413a"/>
<lb n="0413a01"/><p>次結大輪壇印。左手覆之。橫於胸前。右手仰
<lb n="0413a02"/>之。累置於左手上。八輪各相叉。即是。真言
<lb n="0413a03"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0413a04"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;折囉<note place="inline">二合</note>斫羯囉吽<note n="0413001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惹＝弱【甲】</note><app n="0413001"><lem>惹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">弱</rdg></app>吽&CB00680;斛</p>
<lb n="0413a05"/><p>結此印及誦真言。置心前誦真言三遍。即面
<lb n="0413a06"/>向下按地。次印<note n="0413002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曼＝漫【乙】</note><app n="0413002"><lem>曼</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">漫</rdg></app>荼羅。次印上方。次印額。
<lb n="0413a07"/>次印喉。但置口。時一度唼印。<note n="0413003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝面【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413003"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">面</rdg></app>如入口之
<lb n="0413a08"/>勢。而散之。</p>
<lb n="0413a09"/><p>次觀界道。先結五股印。二羽合掌二水二風。
<lb n="0413a10"/>各外相叉。二地二空。各直&CB00594;勿相著。二中指
<lb n="0413a11"/>直&CB00594;如針。是其印相也。以印當心當觀曼荼
<lb n="0413a12"/>羅。內院有五色界道。而周匝莊嚴。作<note n="0413004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝是【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413004"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>觀
<lb n="0413a13"/>已當觀囉字白色。即<note n="0413005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔誦〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413005"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0413006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413006"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>字一遍。以印自
<lb n="0413a14"/>東北角。右繞一匝。次<note n="0413007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝觀【乙】</note><app n="0413007"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg></app><note n="0413008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00772;＝覽【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0413008"><lem>&CB00772;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">覽</rdg></app>字赤色。一誦一
<lb n="0413a15"/>匝如前。次觀迦字黃色。一誦一匝如上。次觀
<lb n="0413a16"/>麼字青色。一誦一匝如上。次觀訶字黑色。一
<lb n="0413a17"/>誦一匝如上。即誦五字真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413a18"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三<note n="0413009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝漫【乙】</note><app n="0413009"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">漫</rdg></app>多沒馱喃囉<app type="＊" source="0413008"><lem>&CB00772;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">覽</rdg></app>迦麼訶</p>
<lb n="0413a19"/><p>次結召請印。二羽內縛。舒右頭指微屈如鉤。
<lb n="0413a20"/>誦真言七遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413a21"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱喃&CB00680;</p>
<lb n="0413a22"/><p>次獻閼伽。二手作合掌。<note n="0413010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二風〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413010"><lem>二風</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>二空端相<app type="＊" source="0412016"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0413a23"/>餘輪散開微屈。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413a24"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三<note n="0413011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曼＝滿【乙】＊</note><app n="0413011"><lem>曼</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">滿</rdg></app>多沒馱喃&CB00344;&CB00344;曩三麼<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0413012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三麼〕－【甲】</note><app n="0413012"><lem>三麼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0413a25"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0413a26"/><p>次結花座印。如前閼伽契。即誦真言三遍。真
<lb n="0413a27"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413a28"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三<app type="＊" source="0413011"><lem>曼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">滿</rdg></app>多沒馱<app type="＊" source="0412027"><lem>喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">南</rdg></app>阿<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0413a29"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。獲得十地滿足。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0413b" n="0413b"/>
<lb n="0413b01"/><p>次結塗香印。右手五輪直&CB00594;。以掌向外。以左
<lb n="0413b02"/>手握右腕。誦真言三遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413b03"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0413013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（曩莫…曰）六十字∞（曩曰…曰）六十六字【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0413013" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（曩莫…曰）六十字∞（曩曰…曰）六十六字【甲】【乙】</note>曩莫三<note n="0413014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝漫【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413014"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">漫</rdg></app>多沒馱喃盪<note n="0413015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疑＝假【甲】</note><app n="0413015"><lem>疑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">假</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0413b04"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。獲得如來五分無漏
<lb n="0413b05"/>法身具足。</p>
<lb n="0413b06"/><p>次結花印。二羽八輪內縛。開掌仰上。以二頭
<lb n="0413b07"/>指。側相<app type="＊" source="0412016"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>。誦真言三遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413b08"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0413016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（曩莫…曰）六十字∞（曩曰…曰）六十六字【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0413016" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（曩莫…曰）六十字∞（曩曰…曰）六十六字【甲】【乙】</note>曩莫三漫多<note n="0413017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沒＋（&CB00499;）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413017"><lem>沒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">沒&CB00499;</rdg></app>喃&CB00135;&CB00135;</p>
<lb n="0413b09"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。獲得如來無礙智具
<lb n="0413b10"/>足。</p>
<lb n="0413b11"/><p>次結燒香印。二羽仰掌。舒立地水火。令背相
<lb n="0413b12"/>附。二風端相<app type="＊" source="0412016"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">柱</rdg></app>。以二空各附風指傍。誦真
<lb n="0413b13"/>言三遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413b14"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三曼多沒馱喃&CB00344;弭</p>
<lb n="0413b15"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。速<note n="0413018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獲＋（得）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413018"><lem>獲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">獲得</rdg></app>如來三十二相
<lb n="0413b16"/>八十種好身。</p>
<lb n="0413b17"/><p>次結飲食印。二羽舒掌。右掌仰覆左掌上。誦
<lb n="0413b18"/>真言三遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413b19"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三<note n="0413019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曼＝漫【甲】</note><app n="0413019"><lem>曼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">漫</rdg></app>多沒馱喃補而曳<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0413b20"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。獲得法喜禪悅食。</p>
<lb n="0413b21"/><p>次結燈明印。左手作拳置腰。右手亦作拳。舒
<lb n="0413b22"/>中指直&CB00594;。誦真言三遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413b23"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三曼多沒馱<note n="0413020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃＋（惹）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413020"><lem>喃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">喃惹</rdg></app><note n="0413021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仡＝紇【甲】</note><app n="0413021"><lem>仡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">紇</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0413b24"/><p>由結此印及誦真言故。速獲得如來清淨五
<lb n="0413b25"/>眼。</p>
<lb n="0413b26"/><p>次作金剛合掌誦讚。普賢行願歎揚於本尊。
<lb n="0413b27"/>及結前佛眼印。誦明而加持五處。</p>
<lb n="0413b28"/><p>次結加持念珠印。二羽月中入珠。加持七遍。
<lb n="0413b29"/>真言曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0413c" n="0413c"/>
<lb n="0413c01"/><p type="dharani">唵尾盧舍那麼<note n="0413022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00256;＝囉【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413022"><lem>&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0413023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><app n="0413023"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0413c02"/><p>次以右手握念珠。置左掌中。即置入合掌中。
<lb n="0413c03"/>誦千轉真言。加持七遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413c04"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>獄呬耶<note place="inline">二合</note>惹<note place="inline">引</note>跛三摩曳<note place="inline">引</note>吽</p>
<lb n="0413c05"/><p>修行者入三摩地觀。閉目運心。專注一緣觀
<lb n="0413c06"/>於本尊。不遠不近。懸念至誠誦本明。不急不
<lb n="0413c07"/>緩不高不下。真言字句。令一一分明。若三時
<lb n="0413c08"/>若四時。若百八遍若千八十為限。遍數畢。作
<lb n="0413c09"/><note n="0413024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">供養＝恭敬【甲】</note><app n="0413024"><lem>供養</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">恭敬</rdg></app>法。然後本尊諸尊奉送於本宮。是則最
<lb n="0413c10"/>上深密之法。忘勿傳授。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0413c11"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三曼多沒馱喃穆婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0411032"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0413025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【乙】</note><app n="0413025"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0413c12"/><p type="W">　已上是金剛手所說。<note n="0413026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已下〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413026"><lem>已下</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0413027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＋（故）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413027"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">是故</rdg></app>世尊印
<lb n="0413c13"/>可言。</p>
<lb n="0413c14"/><p>如是祕密主如汝所說。又祕密主。若說諸聖
<lb n="0413c15"/>尊曼荼羅位諸尊形相。當知亦爾。是則先佛
<lb n="0413c16"/>所<note n="0413028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說〕－【甲】</note><app n="0413028"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。後有佛又推廣其義。如往所說。諸尊
<lb n="0413c17"/>若云黃色者。此是金剛色身。當在因陀羅方
<lb n="0413c18"/>輪中。若白色者。是性淨慈悲色。當在圓壇中。
<lb n="0413c19"/>若赤色者。此是威猛除障色。當在三角中。若
<lb n="0413c20"/>黑色者。此是劫<note n="0413029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">災＝火【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413029"><lem>災</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">火</rdg></app>大風色。當在半月中。若
<lb n="0413c21"/>青<note n="0413030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔色〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413030"><lem>色</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>者。此是虛空不壞不可降伏色。當是忿
<lb n="0413c22"/>怒持明<note n="0413031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413031"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>等。或<note n="0413032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413032"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三角或<note n="0413033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝有【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413033"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>半月中。如色
<lb n="0413c23"/>又曼荼羅者。當知形相亦爾。若<note n="0413034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">黃＝黑【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413034"><lem>黃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">黑</rdg></app>色者。當
<lb n="0413c24"/>作勝進法喜之容。若白色者。<note n="0413035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔當作〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413035"><lem>當作</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>慈悲寂定
<lb n="0413c25"/>之容。若赤色者。當作威猛精進之容。若黑
<lb n="0413c26"/><note n="0413036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">色＋（者）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413036"><lem>色</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">色者</rdg></app>。當作大力奮<note n="0413037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迅＝進【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413037"><lem>迅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">進</rdg></app>之容。若青色者。當作不
<lb n="0413c27"/>可沮壞之容。若黃白色者。<note n="0413038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（則）＋是【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413038"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">則是</rdg></app>兼增益威猛之
<lb n="0413c28"/>容。如是以類推之。乃至種種間雜者。<note n="0413039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔只〕－【甲】，只＝亦【乙】</note><app n="0413039"><lem>只</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">亦</rdg></app>當
<lb n="0413c29"/>隨事甄明<note n="0413040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知其＝其知【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0413040"><lem>知其</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">其知</rdg></app>性分。乃至十方三世諸佛。一
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0981.0414a" n="0414a"/>
<lb n="0414a01"/>切祕密藏中設不說者。亦當通用此意以起
<lb n="0414a02"/>相應事業。故引先佛為證明。法爾通<note n="0414001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔用〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0414001"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>同。
<lb n="0414a03"/>非我出興于世獨作如是說也。修瑜伽者宜
<lb n="0414a04"/>知意行道。若念誦畢。則護身出堂。印佛印
<lb n="0414a05"/><note n="0414002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01244;＝塔【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0414002"><lem>&CB01244;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">塔</rdg></app>兼明本尊瑜伽。然後隨意經行。</p>
<lb n="0414a06"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>大毘盧遮那佛眼修行儀軌<note n="0414003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書曰一點了保安四年七月二十七日書了交了，乙本奧書曰奉交了&SD-A5E7;之本</note></jhead></juan></div1>
